  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the fernbrake, kimchi, vinegar, soy sauce, black pepper, and salt, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes, or until the chicken is cooked through and the sauce has thickened.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve hot over steamed rice or vegetables."
